Digital Real Estate Platform

Welcome to the Digital Real Estate Platform! This project leverages modern technologies to offer secure transactions, thorough verifications, VR home tours, rental history, multiple language support, clear price breakdowns, and detailed neighborhood analytics.


How to Use:

1. Sign Up / Log In: Create an account or log in if you already have one.
2. Search Properties: Use the search functionality to find properties that match your criteria.
3. VR Tour: Click on the VR Tour button to experience a virtual tour of the property.
4. Verify Documents: Upload and verify your documents securely using DigiLocker.
5. Review Rental History: Check the rental history of the property.
6. Check Price Breakdown: View a clear and detailed price breakdown of the property.
7. Neighborhood Analytics: Explore detailed neighborhood analytics to better understand the surrounding area.
8. Secure Transaction: Proceed with the secure transaction to finalize your purchase.


How to Set Up:

Installation:
1. Clone the Repository:
 git clone https://github.com/yourusername/digital-real-estate.git
cd digital-real-estate
2. Open the Project: Open the project in your preferred code editor.
3. Launch the Application: Open the index.html file in your web browser to start using the application.


Technologies Used:

HTML: Markup language for structuring the content.
CSS: Style sheet language for designing the layout and appearance.
JavaScript: Programming language for adding interactive functionalities.

